ivardefs.name: compartment_
ivardefs.desc: An absolute URI which is a reference to the definition of a compartment that the system supports. The reference is to a CompartmentDefinition resource by its canonical URL .

ivardefs.name: documentation
ivardefs.desc: Information about the system's restful capabilities that apply across all applications, such as security.

ivardefs.name: interaction_
ivardefs.desc: A specification of restful operations supported by the system.

ivardefs.name: mode
ivardefs.desc: Identifies whether this portion of the statement is describing the ability to initiate or receive restful operations.

ivardefs.name: resource_
ivardefs.desc: A specification of the restful capabilities of the solution for a specific resource type.

properties.desc: A definition of the restful capabilities of the solution, if any.
